-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Wash your hands thoroughly.</p><p>Use the prep pad to wipe away oil, water, and any other moisture</p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706530212243" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706530212243"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Sweet, oils, creams, and any other moisture present on your natural nails will reduce nail strip adhesion.</p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1705312628125" data-id="1705312628125"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706530212177" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1706530212177" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/2ec836c2-a093-4827-823d-6b2e9f55eb4f/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/mask-group-2-1652835300652_1200x.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="863" height="797" natural-width="863" natural-height="797"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706530212233" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1706530212233"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>2. Apply</p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1706530212264" class="element-wrap" data-i